                                                <p>Using Hi-Definition MicroSpeakers to deliver full-range audio, the ergonomic and lightweight design of the SE210 earphones is ideal for premium on-the-go listening on your iPod or iPhone. They offer the most accurate audio reproduction from both portable and home stereo audio sources--for the ultimate in precision highs and rich low end. In addition, the flexible design allows you to choose the most comfortable fit from a variety of wearing positions.</p>
